年必loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撞低黎隻靈獸大叫果下最精彩</blockquote><br />\n麒麟: This is Sparta!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8ccdbb30b608f13796b45d2d5296d3b27dc4e5","tid":100492,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"你看葉劉仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57c035f8ac4afd119855dd3a844c7adf66bfbec","tid":100492,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明都經歷過咁多次選舉<br />\n點解仲會有人唔知《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳<br />\n<br />\n解籤佬點解會衰？<br />\n<br />\n文章話佢比麒麟撞會衰三年 贏面細姐<br />\n又唔係叫人唔好投佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1829687d11dd621392a26b0f86f1ef8b336ba5b7","tid":100492,"uid":25889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩行過車公廟 個解籤師父排哂隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41072cf40a93972b4893a57a78c181501af5fcd","tid":100492,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"好心佢收下把口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5940852f947d8545dc68366e47fa9fd7707f87","tid":100492,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衰三年根本不在簽文之內,解簽佬鍾意加鹽加醋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比麒麟撞都係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪真係比麒麟撞衰三年就睇你信唔信姐<br />\n咁都犯法？<br />\n風水野不嬲都係信就有 不信就無嫁啦"},{"pid":"af1413055ac92e265505d94c58aede4276a608ff","tid":100492,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗告埋隻麒麟？"},{"pid":"0cb4370a4629d13dd7b2616a52221f0de7ecf26c","tid":100492,"uid":24350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:32:06.000Z","msg":"嘩小家到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce163d3be06ef28c7d36903e0f228a63de6d7b9","tid":100492,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小氣，但其實無講錯<br />\n《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》非一般的嚴格</blockquote><br />\n解籤佬發言竟然會影響選舉結果，咁林鄭日日比人批評佢唔識做show又離地，咪全部報紙網媒都拉得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你點批評法<br />\n<br />\n過往大把人,媒體俾人告，而且係告入左<br />\n你唔知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到大巴把呀？睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f280243517dc65fc4e0299fbc1caa99c057c17","tid":100492,"uid":31229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9846af1e67c3a8d2e2e1d24b2294f43d862dc661","tid":100492,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48efbd7f6a4c49ad61f8426e3e4e96255c36cb15","tid":100492,"uid":31229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a394b741c5dea0bd7185659a33a6084221557ceb","tid":100492,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>明明都經歷過咁多次選舉<br />\n點解仲會有人唔知《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳<br />\n<br />\n解籤佬點解會衰？<br />\n<br />\n文章話佢比麒麟撞會衰三年 贏面細姐<br />\n又唔係叫人唔好投佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》第16條指出，任何人均不得發布任何<span style=\"color: red;\">關於某候選人或某些候選人且屬虛假達關鍵程度或具誤導性達關鍵程度的事實陳<br />\n述</span>，藉以促使或阻礙該候選人或該些候選人當選。<br />\n衰係紅字果度<br />\n<br />\n風水預言唔會係陳述事實，而且佢係幫支簽解讀，<br />\n支簽無講咁講而佢講得太多，淨係任佢UP(當然呢個係風水佬既責任)<br />\n<br />\n其實假設件事放大一百倍就得，如果有競爭對手請左十幾廿個風水佬<br />\n日日係報紙／媒體唱衰話：XXX當選，香港衰足三年！<br />\n連續三個月日唱夜唱瘋狂唱衰佢，其實會有效果<br />\n<br />\n但就呢單野黎講，入就多數告得入<br />\n只係罪行輕微，告得入都唔會太嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔撐葉劉／林鄭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會用錯例子？<br />\n<br />\nxxx當選 香港衰足三年就明顯係指住條友黎唱 叫人唔好投佢<br />\n<br />\n但而家係  葉劉真係比麒麟撞到<br />\n<br />\n我唔知係風水學睇係咪真係會衰三年<br />\n<br />\n個解籤佬只係講返件事出黎（比麒麟撞衰三年係真既話）<br />\n<br />\n咁樣都算係誤導性陳述？<br />\n<br />\n何況只係話佢勝率低姐 無講到巴打你所用既例子<br />\n<br />\nbtw 佢入左閘成為候選人未？"}]}